Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA為何會如此美好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家為何會如此美好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為 大家都在心中收藏著美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 我還想繼續與更多的人邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 昨天的一場雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓今天的威尼斯披上了雪白的外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像為迎接即將到來的新年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給城市換上的新裝一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏姐姐 AQUA很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想更深地去體會那裏夏日的炎熱和冬天的寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但AQUA實在太遠 我一個人無法前往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪白的新威尼斯 一定很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 我過去也有過跟小愛一樣的想法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我 是那時的我想要成為的我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.30,0:01:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 差不多到時間去參加共同練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:38.23,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(320,280)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 雪白的溫馨城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 藍華 香草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直溫暖到心裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這雪下得還真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個晚上就積了這麼厚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像新威尼斯城重生了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒聽到「啊～」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 燈裏小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 藍華 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們小時候想要變成什麼樣的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 突然問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是突然想到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能沒太想過這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為小後輩還是小孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已經不是愛哭鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也已經不是愛哭鬼了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目標 果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像艾莉西亞前輩一樣的優雅女性啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又會被晃前輩罵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為領航員的話 我還是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但艾莉西亞前輩還是我憧憬的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏前輩怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也要變成艾莉西亞前輩那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學別人 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你可別小看了艾莉西亞前輩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要變成那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要相當的努力和毅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白嗎 毅力哦 毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏你沒有的吧 毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在想別的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩以前想變成什麼樣的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是個優雅的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如我們去散步吧 燈裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,積了這麼厚的雪 大概不會有客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就打烊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼出發啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又開始有點冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好暖和…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暖包包 送給燈裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 燈裏你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 這條路還沒有人走過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是第一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩小時候想成為什麼樣的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得很大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 叔叔也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾到這麼大應該夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不謝不謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…那艾莉西亞前輩想變成什麼樣的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 不好意思 那個雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以加入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次滾這麼大的雪球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了 我玩得非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上坡路很難滾呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親愛的 要用力推哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擺到哪都不會丟人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝二位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我們馬上把它移走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 不用不用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就放在那裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次見到這麼大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你們倆做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多人都幫過忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那也讓我們來幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要玩～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領航員小姐們 累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝點暖和的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真的 好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請用 很暖和的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 純白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是白可可哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用白巧克力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手一定很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在做三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃點小蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也去幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要玩得太瘋喊腰痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥 這個不瘋怎麼行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要把它弄得更大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我們再多做一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 三彈嗎 不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 剛才的領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經滾得這麼大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也在幫忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那爸爸也再來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼幫忙啊 這本來就是領航員小姐的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領航員小姐真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了就用這個來裝飾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝飾裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊對了 我還有些好看的布頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是滾雪球 卻能邂逅很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得自己被大家所溫暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越來越喜歡這個城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪的時候 我總是會去滾雪球玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始滾雪球啊 總是會有人跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起幫我把雪球越滾越大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到最後 大家都會很滿足地回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時侯啊 我突然想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想變成那樣的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個微笑 就如水之精靈一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有這麼一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記了時間的流逝 看得入了迷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩果然是個美好的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼突然說這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你與我相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給了我這麼難能可貴的邂逅的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫柔地守護著我的這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏姐姐 我長大以後一定要去新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候燈裏姐姐一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪白的城市非常美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像艾莉西亞小姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 AQUA今天也很和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在感謝本大爺嗎 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿帕爺爺 有人送了好吃的年糕給我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我也繼續在空中遨遊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要世界上還存在包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 藍華 我們去吃披薩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 晃前輩請客嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可以考慮請你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 太好了 我去我去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 總有一天我會要你加倍奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你成為正式領航員之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 天氣暖和起來後 我們去野餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.61,0:22:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密 不過是個很好的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那燈裏想變成什麼樣的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候想要成為精靈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.26,0:23:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 自由地在世界上飛舞 讓大家都得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏馬上也能成為精靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:45.24,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1400,0)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}希望 這座城市的溫馨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.24,0:23:47.87,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1400,0)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}能夠傳達到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.87,0:23:54.45,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1400,2400)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}許多人的心中…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:02:03.47,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:17.62,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:33.33,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:46.78,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:55.95,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:04.26,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:12.60,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:16.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:24.25,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:02:03.47,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:17.62,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}灑落在 舒睡的睫毛間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:33.33,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}讓輕拂的風吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:46.78,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}枝葉間滑落的陽光 映襯你的睡顏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:55.95,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雖是個平凡無奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:04.26,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艷麗的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:12.60,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是與你邂逅的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:16.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我並非孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:24.25,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}因為 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.84,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}手のひらの上に そっとのせた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:08.35,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}やさしさを あたためて そっと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:12.19,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}口ずさんだ 秘密のメロヂィー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:20.23,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}歌ってよ 行くあてもないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:24.30,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}でも 降り出した雨も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:30.84,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}気にしない ずっとそばにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:39.55,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いくつもの虹 越えて行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ふたりで オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:50.66,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな光 星に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:56.07,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}叶えてよ きっと 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:24.03,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いくつもの虹 越えて行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:27.70,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ふたりで オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:35.37,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな光 星に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:38.78,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}叶えてよ きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:46.55,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}描いてた夢 叶えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:49.85,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつかは オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:57.66,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨上がりの虹 見上げた空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:03.60,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}はばたいて いつか 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:11.94,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}胸いっぱいの愛を 集めてよ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:18.72,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心にはいつも愛を 越えてくわ きっとレインボー
